OL,3,C'Request for police reinforcements
OL,4,Creality check for politicians'
OL,6,FFormer senior police officer Jon
OL,7,FBurrows has told UTV the PSNI's
OL,8,Frequest for assistance from Police
OL,9,FScotland should act as a sobering
OL,10,Freality check, and he has urged
OL,11,Fpoliticians to ensure that policing is
OL,12,Ffunded properly.
OL,14,FDozens of Scottish officers are
OL,15,Farriving in Northern Ireland to
OL,16,Fbolster the ranks of the PSNI. The
OL,17,Fforce has been stretched as they deal
OL,18,Fwith the ongoing disorder.
