OL,6,FOfficer numbers in the PSNI sit at
OL,7,F6,300, ` well below the 7,500
OL,8,Frecommended in the Patten Review more
OL,9,Fthan 20 years ago.
OL,11,F"I think the Executive and the
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland Policing Board need
OL,13,Fto ask serious questions for
OL,14,Fthemselves," said Burrows.
