OL,3,C'Request for police reinforcements
OL,4,Creality check for politicians'
OL,6,F"They've let the police now get into
OL,7,Fthis state where we need support from
OL,8,FPolice Scotland to deal with what was
OL,9,Frelatively limited, although high
OL,10,Fimpact violence and mutually isn't the
OL,11,Fanswer, because by the time you get
OL,12,Fpublic order officers in from
OL,13,FScotland, it takes a week.
OL,15,F"And now that public order has
OL,16,Fdissipated, thanks to the good
OL,17,Finvestigative work by the PSNI, so
OL,18,Fmutually, it's not the answer. The
OL,19,Fanswer is a well and properly
OL,20,Fresourced police service."
