OL,3,C'Request for police reinforcements
OL,4,Creality check for politicians'
OL,6,FUUP leader Doug Beattie said
OL,7,F"fundamental change" is needed to
OL,8,Fensure the PSNI is adequately
OL,9,Fresourced.
OL,11,F"The headline is that our police,
OL,12,Fwhich should be sitting at 7,500
OL,13,Fofficers according to the Patten
OL,14,FReview of Policing, is actually
OL,15,Fsitting at 6,300 officers," he said.
