OL,3,C'Request for police reinforcements
OL,4,Creality check for politicians'
OL,6,F"Yet that doesn't tell the whole story
OL,7,Fbecause from that 6,300 you need to
OL,8,Fremove those on long-term or short-
OL,9,Fterm sick, those on maternity leave
OL,10,Fand those either assigned to an
OL,11,Fimportant desk job or are close to
OL,12,Fretirement.
OL,14,F"The available 'officers on the beat'
OL,15,Ffigure is likely to be below 6,000.
OL,16,FThis creates an unbearable pressure on
OL,17,Fthe force and on individual officers
OL,18,Fwho are asked to do more with less."
