OL,6,FHe added: "If politicians in Northern
OL,7,FIreland are not willing to stand up
OL,8,Fand address this then we cannot
OL,9,Fcomplain when our Chief Constable
OL,10,Fgrabs the nettle and delves into the
OL,11,Fpolitical arena to save the force he
OL,12,Fcommands.
OL,14,F"This is a line in the sand for
OL,15,Fpolicing in Northern Ireland, we need
OL,16,Ffundamental change, including direct
OL,17,Fsupport from the Home Office.
